OL,3,CParents jailed after death of
OL,4,Cseriously-ill son in Birmingham
OL,6,FA couple from Birmingham have been
OL,7,Fjailed following the death of their
OL,8,Fseriously-ill so.
OL,10,FTamara and Damion Thomas were
OL,11,Fsentenced following the death of
OL,12,FJoshua Thomas in 2022.
OL,14,FJoshua, who was 12, had displayed
OL,15,Fsymptoms of severe diabetic
OL,16,Fketoacidosis which should have been
OL,17,Fnoticeable for several hours leading
OL,18,Fup to his death.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
