OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782233278
OL,3,CParents jailed after death of
OL,4,Cseriously-ill son in Birmingham
OL,6,FHis parents noticed he was ill, but
OL,7,FTamara Thomas only called 999 some
OL,8,Fhours later after noticing his lips
OL,9,Fhad turned white.
OL,11,FJoshua was taken to hospital on
OL,12,FDecember 9, 2022, but died in the
OL,13,Fearly hours of the following day.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
