OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782233278
OL,3,CParents jailed after death of
OL,4,Cseriously-ill son in Birmingham
OL,6,FLead investigator Vicki Harris, of
OL,7,FWest Midlands Police, said: "Both
OL,8,Fparents were aware of the signs and
OL,9,Fsymptoms of diabetes and expert
OL,10,Fmedical evidence showed their son's
OL,11,Fdeath would have been preventable if
OL,12,Fmedical attention had been sought
OL,13,Fearlier.
OL,15,F"This has been an emotive
OL,16,Finvestigation for everyone involved
OL,17,Fand this verdict is the result of more
OL,18,Fthan three years work examining
OL,19,Fcomplex medical evidence."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
