PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782233278
OL,3,CParents jailed after death of
OL,4,Cseriously-ill son in Birmingham
OL,6,FBoth Tamara and Damion Thomas were
OL,7,Fcharged with gross negligence
OL,8,Fmanslaughter and neglect.
OL,10,FTamara was found guilty of both
OL,11,Fcharges and sentenced to three years
OL,12,Fand nine months in prison.
OL,14,FDamion was found not guilty of
OL,15,Fmanslaughter, but guilty of neglect.
OL,16,FHe was jailed for two years and nine
OL,17,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
